 freyja3d 0.10.0, Kagura alpha ( Development branch )
 =====================================================================

 Kagura alpha, 0.10.0.0

 * Pick ray support.
 * 3d cursor support.
 * Edit mode support.
 * Viewport separation support for mouse events.

 * Camera support.

 * Arcball implementation to remove legacy vector angles.

 * Merge most of FreyjaRender with freyja3d::OpenGL.

